ism', 'Brivaracetam, Topiramate, Ezogabine, Lamotrigine, Ethosuximide, Lacosamide, Levetiracetam, Tiagabine, Clonazepam, Paramethadione, Perampanel, More', 'Cabazitaxel, Vinblastine, Topotecan, Teniposide, Vinorelbine', 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/89351/', '[1] "Product Information. Yondelis (trabectedin)." Janssen Pharmaceuticals, Titusville, NJ.[2] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[3] "Product Information. Yondelis (trabectedin)." Janssen Pharmaceuticals, Titusville, NJ.[4] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0', 1767369485);
